title: no two APPLY targets should have the same name
query: In rooms dataset rooms grouped by Address and Full Name and Furniture, find entries whose Furniture includes "Movable" and Furniture does not include "Fixed"; show Address and Full Name and Furniture and maxSeats and minSeats, where maxSeats is the MAX of Seats and maxSeats is the MIN of Seats; sort in descending order by Address and Full Name and Furniture and maxSeats and minSeats.
